description: C’est Cheese is serving up amazing gourmet grilled cheese sandwiches on the streets of Cincinnati.This big bus is dishing big flavors in their every innovative creation. Once you try a taste of these made-to-order meals, you’ll instantly see why C’est Cheese has been rated Cincinnati’s Best Truck for the last three years.Their rotating selection of local favorites includes The Bee Sting (with mozzarella, pepperoni & basil infused honey with chili flaked butter), Bacon Me Crazy (with mozzarella, bacon, spinach & sun-dried tomato spread), and CheesyQue (BBQ pulled pork & cheddar), to name a few.For all this and much more (like delicious homemade pickles!), head straight to C’est Cheese and savor these ooey gooey, smile-worthy delights.
name: C'est Cheese
